[~zxu], Can you look into this checkstyle issue in the patch?
{code:xml}
-1	checkstyle	3m 58s	The applied patch generated 1 additional checkstyle issues.
{code}

The last Jenkins run didn't have checkstyle issue. The only difference between these two patches is an import statement:
{code}
import com.google.common.annotations.VisibleForTesting;
{code}
It looks like the import statement causes this checkstyle issue. But this import statement  looks good to me.
Don't know why the checkstyle script report this issue. So it looks like a script issue.
